Project Instructions:

Prerequisites:
Ensure that you have Node.js installed on your system.

Steps:
1. Update Node.js to the latest version.
2. Install dependencies by running:
   
   npm install
   
   Or install individual dependencies using:
   
   npm install bcryptjs express hbs jsonwebtoken mongoose
  
3. Start the development server by running:
   
   npm run dev
   
4. Open your web browser and navigate to:
   http://localhost:3005
   
5. If the directories are not available, manually check by routing to:
   
   http://localhost:3005/bank (eg.)
   

